1
00:00:22,740 --> 00:00:29,660
♪In the stormy night♪

2
00:00:30,620 --> 00:00:37,340
♪The dark hair of a charming woman
is reflected in the flame of a candle♪

3
00:00:37,900 --> 00:00:41,300
♪Shrouded by year after year of memories♪

4
00:00:41,980 --> 00:00:45,780
♪I can do nothing
but feign indifference♪

5
00:00:46,220 --> 00:00:53,140
♪Outlining your cheeks♪

6
00:00:53,740 --> 00:00:55,540
♪Together and apart, just like quicksand♪

7
00:00:55,740 --> 00:00:57,420
♪I'm meant to make peace with myself♪

8
00:00:57,660 --> 00:01:01,140
♪Rebuild or crumble♪

9
00:01:01,420 --> 00:01:03,780
♪Drift away in the clouds♪

10
00:01:04,060 --> 00:01:05,660
♪Driving away♪

11
00:01:06,020 --> 00:01:09,300
♪Your dashing pretense♪

12
00:01:09,660 --> 00:01:11,620
♪A drunken dream♪

13
00:01:11,940 --> 00:01:13,500
♪A person I miss♪

14
00:01:13,860 --> 00:01:16,860
♪Of course I know if it's real♪

15
00:01:17,060 --> 00:01:21,660
♪Even if you're just by my side♪

16
00:01:22,180 --> 00:01:28,220
♪I want to hold on to you
but I can only play dumb♪

17
00:01:29,940 --> 00:01:35,060
[In Blossom]

18
00:01:36,020 --> 00:01:38,820
[Episode 17]

19
00:01:53,590 --> 00:01:54,310
Young Lady.

20
00:01:55,480 --> 00:01:58,190
This pot of black magnolia
is very valuable.

21
00:01:58,590 --> 00:02:00,870
Young Master had brought it
all the way here from the capital.

22
00:02:01,440 --> 00:02:02,950
This is the last pot left.

23
00:02:03,120 --> 00:02:03,950
If you want to pick a flower,

24
00:02:04,160 --> 00:02:05,720
you should pick some other flowers
in the garden, okay?

25
00:02:15,320 --> 00:02:16,000
Ling,

26
00:02:17,000 --> 00:02:19,390
Doesn't brother own a few shops in Heyang?

27
00:02:20,240 --> 00:02:23,000
Yes, the Shangguan family's business
is spread all over the world

28
00:02:23,240 --> 00:02:24,630
and we deal in all sorts of trade.

29
00:02:24,910 --> 00:02:26,270
Then go and ask the shopkeepers

30
00:02:26,360 --> 00:02:28,030
if they have noticed

31
00:02:28,240 --> 00:02:29,390
a ripple pattern,

32
00:02:29,800 --> 00:02:31,190
whether it's on an artifact
or something else.

33
00:02:31,520 --> 00:02:32,630
Finders will be handsomely rewarded.

34
00:02:34,000 --> 00:02:35,830
Also, go to a bookstore

35
00:02:36,160 --> 00:02:37,800
and buy all the historical records

36
00:02:37,830 --> 00:02:39,270
related to Heyang.

37
00:02:40,110 --> 00:02:40,880
Yes.

38
00:02:41,030 --> 00:02:41,670
Young Lady.

39
00:02:42,320 --> 00:02:44,800
Young Lady, a fisherman
visited us just now.

40
00:02:44,800 --> 00:02:46,320
He said that someone named Bai Xiaosheng

41
00:02:46,360 --> 00:02:47,360
told him to bring a message.

42
00:02:47,600 --> 00:02:49,240
Bai Xiaosheng is detained at the dock.

43
00:02:49,360 --> 00:02:50,600
She hopes the Young Lady can go
rescue her quickly.

44
00:02:52,080 --> 00:02:54,030
You asked for two hours

45
00:02:54,270 --> 00:02:56,360
so that your relatives could
come to see you for the last time.

46
00:02:57,000 --> 00:02:59,160
Now that the time is up,

47
00:02:59,750 --> 00:03:00,360
jump.

48
00:03:01,630 --> 00:03:03,600
Wait, sir.

49
00:03:03,750 --> 00:03:05,470
I really don't dare to do it again.

50
00:03:05,470 --> 00:03:07,110
Can you give me another chance?

51
00:03:07,190 --> 00:03:09,030
How dare you bribe the boatman

52
00:03:09,080 --> 00:03:11,110
and smuggle cargo on our ships?

53
00:03:13,320 --> 00:03:15,190
Since you had the courage to do so,

54
00:03:16,160 --> 00:03:18,550
you should have expected this day.

55
00:03:19,110 --> 00:03:20,880
Stop dilly-dallying, jump now!

56
00:03:23,360 --> 00:03:25,080
I beg of you, sir.

57
00:03:26,080 --> 00:03:27,030
Don't…

58
00:03:27,470 --> 00:03:28,030
It seems like

59
00:03:28,030 --> 00:03:30,110
- you need my help.
- Stop!

60
00:03:31,960 --> 00:03:34,720
Save me, Caiwei!

61
00:03:35,600 --> 00:03:36,960
How much cargo did she smuggle?

62
00:03:37,080 --> 00:03:38,160
I will compensate you ten times.

63
00:03:39,390 --> 00:03:41,390
Where do you think you're at?

64
00:03:42,110 --> 00:03:43,910
The rules of Silver Rain Terrace

65
00:03:44,160 --> 00:03:46,630
will not be swayed by your coins.

66
00:03:46,830 --> 00:03:47,720
Silver Rain Terrace?

67
00:03:48,260 --> 00:03:49,150
I told you

68
00:03:49,160 --> 00:03:52,080
I am really friends
with your Young Master.

69
00:03:55,800 --> 00:03:58,160
Our Young Master is a wise man.

70
00:03:58,750 --> 00:04:01,600
How could he be friends
with women like you?

71
00:04:03,270 --> 00:04:04,750
They are indeed my friends.

72
00:04:07,110 --> 00:04:08,080
Young Master Zhuo!

73
00:04:15,270 --> 00:04:16,920
Young Master.

74
00:04:18,830 --> 00:04:20,070
- Xiaosheng.
- Caiwei.

75
00:04:20,600 --> 00:04:21,510
I was so scared.

76
00:04:25,830 --> 00:04:26,790
Mr. Zhu, I presume?

77
00:04:27,000 --> 00:04:28,720
You did your job faithfully, well done.

78
00:04:29,200 --> 00:04:29,950
However,

79
00:04:30,200 --> 00:04:31,950
please do me a favor

80
00:04:32,200 --> 00:04:33,070
and let this go.

81
00:04:33,270 --> 00:04:34,000
Young Master,

82
00:04:34,640 --> 00:04:37,040
smuggling goods is no small deal.

83
00:04:37,440 --> 00:04:38,390
Moreover, Silver Rain Terrace

84
00:04:38,480 --> 00:04:39,790
has always maintained the rules.

85
00:04:40,350 --> 00:04:40,920
Young Master,

86
00:04:41,110 --> 00:04:43,950
you shouldn't break the rules
because of an outsider.

87
00:04:44,350 --> 00:04:45,200
You're right.

88
00:04:48,670 --> 00:04:49,790
In the future,

89
00:04:49,790 --> 00:04:51,320
she will be the Young Madam
of Silver Rain Terrace.

90
00:04:51,920 --> 00:04:53,760
Her words are my words.

91
00:04:54,350 --> 00:04:56,200
My words are the rules
of Silver Rain Terrace.

92
00:04:56,640 --> 00:04:59,070
Are you questioning

93
00:04:59,480 --> 00:05:00,440
my words?

94
00:05:01,070 --> 00:05:03,230
Young Master, please forgive me.
I dare not do so.

95
00:05:04,950 --> 00:05:06,830
Young Madam.

96
00:05:15,320 --> 00:05:17,160
Fortunately, you came in time.

97
00:05:18,000 --> 00:05:19,480
By the way, how did you know we were here?

98
00:05:21,390 --> 00:05:23,160
She also sent a message to me.

99
00:05:24,350 --> 00:05:26,790
Well, Little Liar, you really know
how to get into trouble.

100
00:05:26,950 --> 00:05:29,000
Almost every time I see you,
there's some kind of trouble.

101
00:05:30,350 --> 00:05:32,920
It shows that Young Master Zhuo
is a naturally gifted problem solver.

102
00:05:38,320 --> 00:05:40,390
Let's go have a drink together tonight.

103
00:05:41,550 --> 00:05:42,160
Let's go.

104
00:05:43,550 --> 00:05:46,320
Well, I haven't sorted
those goods of mine.

105
00:05:46,550 --> 00:05:47,350
Both of you go ahead.

106
00:05:48,040 --> 00:05:49,640
Caiwei, I will meet you
in the Sunrise Garden later.

107
00:05:52,390 --> 00:05:54,390
Instead of watching the two of you
being lovey-dovey from the sidelines,

108
00:05:54,600 --> 00:05:55,670
I might as well jump into the river.

109
00:05:56,720 --> 00:05:58,160
I'll see you later, Caiwei.

110
00:06:01,950 --> 00:06:03,720
Why is Xiaosheng acting weird lately?

111
00:06:03,920 --> 00:06:05,000
Hasn't she always been like this?

112
00:06:05,200 --> 00:06:06,390
She would rather have money than life.

113
00:06:07,880 --> 00:06:10,640
Jiang, don't do this again.

114
00:06:13,440 --> 00:06:14,110
What?

115
00:06:14,760 --> 00:06:16,640
Didn't I move out from the county yamen?

116
00:06:17,000 --> 00:06:18,830
We won't need these pretenses anymore.

117
00:06:19,070 --> 00:06:20,440
You don't have to hang around me all day.

118
00:06:20,480 --> 00:06:22,270
Stop calling me Young Madam
or something like that.

119
00:06:22,270 --> 00:06:24,830
It's really awkward for me.

120
00:06:26,200 --> 00:06:26,950
This is not a pretense.

121
00:06:27,790 --> 00:06:28,440
I meant it

122
00:06:29,640 --> 00:06:30,440
when I said it.

123
00:06:33,350 --> 00:06:34,040
Before,

124
00:06:34,760 --> 00:06:36,320
I thought I regarded you as a friend.

125
00:06:37,160 --> 00:06:38,040
Two months ago,

126
00:06:38,390 --> 00:06:39,320
when I returned to Heyang,

127
00:06:39,880 --> 00:06:41,510
I was joyful on my way to see you,

128
00:06:43,480 --> 00:06:45,440
but I heard the news of your death.

129
00:06:46,510 --> 00:06:48,040
My mind went blank.

130
00:06:49,830 --> 00:06:52,350
Not even swords have made me
that frightened.

131
00:06:54,110 --> 00:06:55,160
Only then did I understand

132
00:06:55,550 --> 00:06:56,480
you were no longer just a friend

133
00:06:56,480 --> 00:06:57,830
in my heart.

134
00:06:59,950 --> 00:07:00,790
After your return,

135
00:07:01,200 --> 00:07:02,510
every word I said to you,

136
00:07:02,920 --> 00:07:04,000
every act I did,

137
00:07:04,640 --> 00:07:05,880
was all from the heart.

138
00:07:08,230 --> 00:07:09,110
If you are willing,

139
00:07:09,920 --> 00:07:11,110
I'll marry you anytime.

140
00:07:20,760 --> 00:07:21,480
Jiang,

141
00:07:23,830 --> 00:07:25,720
I've always considered you my best friend.

142
00:07:26,640 --> 00:07:27,480
Previously,

143
00:07:28,350 --> 00:07:29,350
now,

144
00:07:30,790 --> 00:07:31,830
and even in the future.

145
00:07:32,790 --> 00:07:33,550
This

146
00:07:34,510 --> 00:07:35,760
will never change.

147
00:07:40,790 --> 00:07:41,720
Determined.

148
00:07:44,230 --> 00:07:45,070
Without hesitation.

149
00:07:47,760 --> 00:07:49,200
I did imagine this,

150
00:07:49,950 --> 00:07:50,880
but I didn't expect it

151
00:07:51,550 --> 00:07:52,480
to feel

152
00:07:53,950 --> 00:07:54,790
much worse

153
00:07:55,350 --> 00:07:56,110
than I imagined.

154
00:07:59,440 --> 00:08:00,880
Compared to disappointment,

155
00:08:01,600 --> 00:08:02,640
a false dawn is even more hurtful.

156
00:08:03,950 --> 00:08:05,920
I regard you as my best friend,

157
00:08:06,600 --> 00:08:08,550
so I can never give you false hope.

158
00:08:27,230 --> 00:08:27,950
Young Master.

159
00:08:34,150 --> 00:08:34,760
Young Master.

160
00:08:35,400 --> 00:08:37,520
Gu Yong is dead
and the Relief Hall has been purged.

161
00:08:37,880 --> 00:08:39,350
Are you still doubting the Four Greats?

162
00:08:40,110 --> 00:08:42,320
I'm thinking about the man
behind the scenes in the capital.

163
00:08:43,150 --> 00:08:45,000
Why is he growing his power in Heyang?

164
00:08:45,520 --> 00:08:47,520
Was it simply to kill people?

165
00:08:49,080 --> 00:08:51,110
I read the accounts booklet
of Relief Hall.

166
00:08:51,760 --> 00:08:53,200
It's true that the only recorded business
was killing.

167
00:08:53,280 --> 00:08:54,400
So I suspect

168
00:08:54,790 --> 00:08:56,110
there must be some of them

169
00:08:56,760 --> 00:08:58,280
still hiding in the Four Greats.

170
00:09:02,550 --> 00:09:04,350
Relief Hall was destroyed,

171
00:09:04,840 --> 00:09:07,910
and there was no movement at all
in the Life and Death House.

172
00:09:08,150 --> 00:09:10,670
Only Silver Rain Terrace
and Hundred Flowers Court are left.

173
00:09:11,080 --> 00:09:12,000
But one of them

174
00:09:12,080 --> 00:09:13,670
is sincerely helping Miss Shangguan.

175
00:09:13,880 --> 00:09:14,520
Another one

176
00:09:14,520 --> 00:09:15,960
has also allied with Young Master early on

177
00:09:16,640 --> 00:09:18,350
to solve
the county yamen's urgent problem.

178
00:09:19,670 --> 00:09:20,520
Well…

179
00:09:21,080 --> 00:09:22,910
I must have missed something.

180
00:09:24,470 --> 00:09:26,000
What is it?

181
00:09:29,230 --> 00:09:30,670
We eat a meal bite by bite,

182
00:09:30,790 --> 00:09:32,110
so we should investigate a case
bit by bit.

183
00:09:32,350 --> 00:09:34,230
Mulling over it is not going to help.

184
00:09:36,670 --> 00:09:37,590
Why don't…

185
00:09:39,670 --> 00:09:41,150
Just tell me what you want to do.

186
00:09:41,640 --> 00:09:42,640
Let's go on horseback.

187
00:10:18,150 --> 00:10:18,960
Miss Qing,

188
00:10:19,760 --> 00:10:21,400
you're looking at this veil again.

189
00:10:24,760 --> 00:10:25,670
It's been nine years.

190
00:10:30,150 --> 00:10:30,760
Oh, right.

191
00:10:31,960 --> 00:10:33,350
How is the county yamen now?

192
00:10:34,440 --> 00:10:35,350
Very quiet.

193
00:10:35,910 --> 00:10:38,550
You may even say it's lifeless.

194
00:10:42,590 --> 00:10:44,350
It has only been two months

195
00:10:44,520 --> 00:10:45,910
since Master Pan came to Heyang.

196
00:10:47,150 --> 00:10:50,150
Yet he's reached this point.

197
00:10:51,030 --> 00:10:52,710
This is beyond my expectations.

198
00:10:53,470 --> 00:10:55,000
I wanted him to quickly

199
00:10:55,000 --> 00:10:56,910
find out the forces behind Gu Yong.

200
00:10:57,440 --> 00:10:59,400
I admit it's an unreasonable task.

201
00:11:01,840 --> 00:11:02,790
Maybe

202
00:11:03,550 --> 00:11:04,550
it's time

203
00:11:05,840 --> 00:11:07,080
to give him a push.

204
00:11:08,220 --> 00:11:11,220
[Sunrise Garden]

205
00:11:11,220 --> 00:11:17,380
[Beautiful things complement each other]

206
00:11:29,590 --> 00:11:31,200
These are not what I want.

207
00:11:32,470 --> 00:11:33,320
Young Lady,

208
00:11:33,550 --> 00:11:35,200
we have bought everything

209
00:11:35,350 --> 00:11:36,760
on the Heyang market

210
00:11:36,910 --> 00:11:38,000
with a ripple pattern here.

211
00:11:38,350 --> 00:11:40,670
We really couldn't find the type
you described.

212
00:11:47,740 --> 00:11:51,300
[Sunrise Garden]

213
00:11:52,520 --> 00:11:54,640
Sir, we have arrived at Sunrise Garden.

214
00:11:55,080 --> 00:11:56,400
I wonder if Miss Shangguan

215
00:11:56,440 --> 00:11:57,670
is doing well here.

216
00:11:57,790 --> 00:11:59,080
Why don't we go in and take a look?

217
00:12:03,710 --> 00:12:06,030
Young Lady, the ripple pattern you want,

218
00:12:06,230 --> 00:12:07,030
I have it here.

219
00:12:07,790 --> 00:12:08,470
Where?

220
00:12:22,030 --> 00:12:24,760
Mr. Chen, the Young Lady
is looking for water ripples.

221
00:12:24,880 --> 00:12:26,710
Why did you bring so many dancers here?

222
00:12:27,670 --> 00:12:28,350
Please, have a look.

223
00:12:47,980 --> 00:12:50,020
[Sunrise Garden]

224
00:12:55,400 --> 00:12:56,110
You heard it.

225
00:12:56,840 --> 00:12:58,520
We don't have to worry about her at all.

226
00:12:59,080 --> 00:12:59,710
Young Master.

227
00:13:00,320 --> 00:13:01,550
We're here already anyway.

228
00:13:01,840 --> 00:13:02,790
Aren't you curious about

229
00:13:02,880 --> 00:13:04,710
how is Miss Shangguan doing in there?

230
00:13:05,590 --> 00:13:07,880
Look how happy Ling is.

231
00:13:08,790 --> 00:13:09,590
Are you envious?

232
00:13:10,470 --> 00:13:11,400
Do you want to move here

233
00:13:11,400 --> 00:13:13,030
and have fun with them?

234
00:13:14,280 --> 00:13:14,910
No.

235
00:13:15,710 --> 00:13:17,110
If not, you should stop loitering here.

236
00:13:18,030 --> 00:13:19,320
Young Master.

237
00:13:22,320 --> 00:13:23,880
What a stubborn man.

238
00:13:31,180 --> 00:13:37,060
[Court]

239
00:13:59,590 --> 00:14:00,320
Young Master,

240
00:14:00,710 --> 00:14:01,520
if…

241
00:14:04,840 --> 00:14:05,590
Sir!

242
00:14:06,790 --> 00:14:07,440
What's wrong?

243
00:14:07,590 --> 00:14:09,400
Mr. Pan, someone set fire
to the death row.

244
00:14:09,640 --> 00:14:10,280
What?

245
00:14:13,400 --> 00:14:14,150
What happened?

246
00:14:16,590 --> 00:14:19,030
Sir, somebody in this cell

247
00:14:19,230 --> 00:14:20,150
knocked over an oil lamp.

248
00:14:20,230 --> 00:14:21,960
Fortunately, the straw was wet,
so there was no fire,

249
00:14:21,960 --> 00:14:22,910
just smoke.

250
00:14:29,470 --> 00:14:31,400
Who on earth is so bold

251
00:14:31,470 --> 00:14:33,590
as to start a fire in the county jail?

252
00:14:33,840 --> 00:14:35,280
We don't know what was going on either.

253
00:14:35,520 --> 00:14:36,880
There were no prisoners held here.

254
00:14:40,590 --> 00:14:41,670
Wet straw.

255
00:14:43,880 --> 00:14:45,200
It wasn't to set a fire

256
00:14:46,350 --> 00:14:47,790
but to make smoke.

257
00:14:49,960 --> 00:14:50,790
They wanted

258
00:14:51,150 --> 00:14:53,080
to attract our attention.

259
00:15:41,280 --> 00:15:43,400
This fire was deliberately
set off by someone.

260
00:15:44,880 --> 00:15:46,670
Sir, that person is very weird,

261
00:15:46,840 --> 00:15:48,110
you shouldn't go near him.

262
00:15:48,550 --> 00:15:49,670
What crime did he commit?

263
00:15:50,030 --> 00:15:51,550
The Ghostly Fire Case.

264
00:16:10,710 --> 00:16:12,520
You're here at such a late hour, Mr. Pan.

265
00:16:12,710 --> 00:16:14,710
How can I serve you?

266
00:16:15,400 --> 00:16:16,670
I'm looking for a dossier.

267
00:16:19,080 --> 00:16:20,080
What dossier?

268
00:16:20,760 --> 00:16:24,110
I'll look for it with you.

269
00:16:24,150 --> 00:16:26,110
No need. I'll look for it myself.

270
00:16:26,550 --> 00:16:27,670
Go back to your room and rest.

271
00:16:29,080 --> 00:16:30,280
Thank you for your hard work, sir.

272
00:17:05,040 --> 00:17:06,400
Shangguan Zhi could always quickly

273
00:17:06,400 --> 00:17:08,000
find the required dossier.

274
00:17:09,040 --> 00:17:10,710
I thought it was a simple task.

275
00:17:12,040 --> 00:17:13,160
Now that I think about it,

276
00:17:13,560 --> 00:17:15,230
she must have put in a lot of effort.

277
00:17:25,940 --> 00:17:27,820
[Ghostly Fire Case Volume 2,
Ghostly Fire Case Volume 1]

278
00:17:31,950 --> 00:17:33,800
The Xinzheng Academy in Heyang

279
