a year ago,

284
00:17:47,950 --> 00:17:50,040
four classmates from Xinzheng Academy,

285
00:17:50,280 --> 00:17:52,470
Chen Fu, Zhou Ge,

286
00:17:52,950 --> 00:17:55,280
Liu Shi, and Shen Ci

287
00:17:55,470 --> 00:17:57,280
were having a courage competition

288
00:17:57,520 --> 00:17:59,000
[Chen Fu, Scholar of Xinzheng Academy]
in the eerie mountain forest.

