00:18:02,820 --> 00:18:05,060
[Liu Shi, Scholar of Xinzheng Academy]

290
00:18:06,340 --> 00:18:08,500
[Zhou Ge, Scholar of Xinzheng Academy]

291
00:18:09,780 --> 00:18:12,500
[Shen Ci, Scholar of Xinzheng Academy]

292
00:18:25,430 --> 00:18:26,560
It's just a few bones.

293
00:18:28,000 --> 00:18:29,000
This doesn't scare me.

294
00:18:29,590 --> 00:18:30,590
If you are afraid,

295
00:18:30,760 --> 00:18:31,950
you should go back as soon as possible.

296
00:18:33,590 --> 00:18:34,710
We are not afraid either.

297
00:18:35,920 --> 00:18:37,680
Yes, we're not afraid.

298
00:18:41,280 --> 00:18:41,920
Let's go.

299
00:18:46,190 --> 00:18:47,070
Who's there?

300
00:18:48,040 --> 00:18:49,070
Pretending to be a ghost?

301
00:18:49,310 --> 00:18:50,560
Show yourself!

302
00:19:02,710 --> 00:19:04,280
- Shen Ci!
- Shen Ci!

303
00:19:26,710 --> 00:19:28,590
- Run! Quick!
- Run!

304
00:19:32,040 --> 00:19:34,920
A ghost!

305
00:19:35,160 --> 00:19:36,830
Shen Ci...

306
00:19:36,950 --> 00:19:38,310
Shen Ci was caught by a ghost.

307
00:19:39,310 --> 00:19:43,760
- Shen Ci!
- Shen Ci!

308
00:19:44,230 --> 00:19:47,230
Shen Ci was not found alive or dead.

309
00:19:47,800 --> 00:19:48,920
Everyone agreed

310
00:19:49,110 --> 00:19:50,830
that Shen Ci had died.

311
00:19:52,070 --> 00:19:53,680
But who would have thought…

312
00:19:59,470 --> 00:20:00,880
- Wait...
- Well...

313
00:20:01,040 --> 00:20:02,000
What happened?

314
00:20:05,070 --> 00:20:06,070
Shen Ci?

315
00:20:06,640 --> 00:20:07,560
You are not dead?

316
00:20:08,040 --> 00:20:09,160
Shen Ci, your eyes...

317
00:20:09,640 --> 00:20:10,800
What's wrong with your eyes?

318
00:20:11,070 --> 00:20:12,920
Come, sit here.

319
00:20:15,590 --> 00:20:17,110
Shen Ci, you…

320
00:20:17,470 --> 00:20:18,760
Weren't you captured by a ghost?

321
00:20:18,760 --> 00:20:20,160
Yes, how did you come back?

322
00:20:20,880 --> 00:20:21,560
Yes.

323
00:20:22,350 --> 00:20:23,590
We all saw it then.

324
00:20:23,760 --> 00:20:25,230
I told you not to go there,
but you insisted.

325
00:20:25,280 --> 00:20:25,920
And then

326
00:20:26,560 --> 00:20:28,280
