327
00:20:28,640 --> 00:20:29,580
- Yeah.
- Yeah.

328
00:20:29,580 --> 00:20:30,120
Yes.

329
00:20:31,280 --> 00:20:32,920
I was dragged into the woods
by an evil spirit.

330
00:20:33,640 --> 00:20:35,680
The evil spirit was about
to drag me into the ground.

331
00:20:35,760 --> 00:20:36,950
I was struggling.

332
00:20:37,070 --> 00:20:38,710
I managed to escape it
by kicking it with my feet.

333
00:20:38,880 --> 00:20:39,640
But

334
00:20:40,950 --> 00:20:42,400
the miasma was thick in the woods.

335
00:20:42,830 --> 00:20:43,520
As soon as I came out,

336
00:20:44,000 --> 00:20:45,160
I couldn't see anything.

337
00:20:48,070 --> 00:20:48,760
Shen Ci.

338
00:20:50,160 --> 00:20:50,710
Shen Ci.

339
00:20:50,920 --> 00:20:53,640
Everyone thought
that this matter was over.

340
00:20:53,950 --> 00:20:55,520
But in the next month,

341
00:20:55,560 --> 00:20:57,430
something unbelievable happened again.

342
00:20:57,590 --> 00:21:02,310
It is not that there is no peaceful abode
but that I have no peaceful heart.

343
00:21:02,590 --> 00:21:07,310
It is not that my wealth is not sufficient
but that my passion yearns for more.

344
00:21:07,560 --> 00:21:11,040
Therefore the superior man is strict
with one's self but lenient with others

345
00:21:11,190 --> 00:21:14,000
while the multitude are lenient
with themselves but strict with others.

346
00:21:14,160 --> 00:21:18,520
It is not that there is no peaceful abode
but that I have no peaceful heart.

347
00:21:18,680 --> 00:21:23,350
It is not that my wealth is not sufficient
but that my passion yearns for more.

348
00:21:23,590 --> 00:21:27,310
It is not that there is no peaceful abode,
or that my wealth is not sufficient...

349
00:21:27,310 --> 00:21:28,310
I can't see.

350
00:21:29,640 --> 00:21:30,950
Why can't I see anything?

351
00:21:33,560 --> 00:21:34,520
Help me.

352
00:21:36,400 --> 00:21:37,920
My eyes!

353
00:21:38,040 --> 00:21:41,280
I can't see either. Fu!

354
00:21:42,350 --> 00:21:43,560
I can't see either.

355
00:21:44,560 --> 00:21:48,040
The three became blind
and stopped eating and drinking.

356
00:21:48,190 --> 00:21:49,590
They became delirious.

357
00:21:49,950 --> 00:21:52,520
Chen Fu's father
was the head of the academy.

358
00:21:52,830 --> 00:21:54,160
He hired famous physicians,

359
00:21:54,760 --> 00:21:56,760
but none could diagnose
the cause of Chen Fu's illness.

360
00:21:57,350 --> 00:21:58,560
It was rumored

361
00:21:58,680 --> 00:22:00,680
that it was caused by ghosts in the woods.

362
00:22:02,070 --> 00:22:03,520
Until one night,

363
00:22:03,800 --> 00:22:05,710
a scholar who got up at night

364
00:22:06,110 --> 00:22:07,160
saw something.

365
00:22:12,310 --> 00:22:13,040
Chen Fu?

366
00:22:13,590 --> 00:22:14,680
Zhou Ge, Liu Shi?

367
00:22:15,160 --> 00:22:16,640
Where are you going?

368
00:22:27,580 --> 00:22:30,580
[Studying is the beginning
of our glorious success]

369
00:22:30,580 --> 00:22:34,620
[Xinzheng Academy]

370
00:23:18,920 --> 00:23:20,110
Chen Fu!

371
00:23:38,730 --> 00:23:40,280
- Chen Fu!
- Zhou Ge!

372
00:23:40,560 --> 00:23:42,430
- Liu Shi!
- Zhou Ge!

373
00:23:43,310 --> 00:23:44,590
Liu Shi!

374
00:23:44,950 --> 00:23:45,980
Chen Fu!

375
00:23:45,980 --> 00:23:48,380
- Zhou Ge!
- Liu Shi!

376
00:23:48,560 --> 00:23:50,760
- Fu!
- Chen Fu! Zhou Ge!

377
00:23:51,430 --> 00:23:52,710
- Fu.
- Where are you?

378
00:23:52,830 --> 00:23:54,470
Chen Fu!

379
00:23:55,880 --> 00:23:56,710
Look.

380
00:23:57,190 --> 00:23:57,830
- Where?
- Chen Fu.

381
00:23:58,000 --> 00:23:58,710
Over there.

382
00:24:00,430 --> 00:24:01,920
- Mr. Chen!
- Sir!

383
00:24:02,160 --> 00:24:02,920
[Mr. Chen, Xinzheng Academy]
Here he is.

384
00:24:03,190 --> 00:24:04,280
Look.

385
00:24:04,590 --> 00:24:06,350
- He's dead.
- What...

386
00:24:10,560 --> 00:24:11,230
What...

387
00:24:13,230 --> 00:24:14,640
What... Fu.

388
00:24:15,680 --> 00:24:16,350
Fu.

389
00:24:20,280 --> 00:24:22,590
Shen Ci.

390
00:24:25,070 --> 00:24:27,230
Shen Ci.

391
00:24:30,800 --> 00:24:31,590
Fu.

392
00:24:36,800 --> 00:24:39,230
Arrest Shen Ci!

393
00:24:41,350 --> 00:24:42,800
It was this ingrate.

394
00:24:43,280 --> 00:24:45,040
Instead of thanking the academy
for cultivating him,

395
00:24:45,430 --> 00:24:47,350
he dabbled in witchcraft and killed my son

396
00:24:47,520 --> 00:24:49,800
and two other innocent lives.

397
00:24:50,520 --> 00:24:51,680
Sir, please judge wisely.

398
00:24:52,230 --> 00:24:54,160
Let Shen Ci pay with his life!

399
00:24:54,470 --> 00:24:56,430
You,

400
00:24:57,280 --> 00:24:58,880
what else do you have to say?

401
00:24:59,070 --> 00:25:00,880
When Chen Fu and others
were possessed by evil spirits,

402
00:25:01,520 --> 00:25:02,950
I was studying in the academy.

403
00:25:03,830 --> 00:25:04,710
I did not go to the back mountain.

404
00:25:06,040 --> 00:25:07,280
Since you know witchcraft,

405
00:25:07,520 --> 00:25:09,680
you could've easily erased your tracks.

406
00:25:10,190 --> 00:25:12,470
You keep saying that I know witchcraft.

407
00:25:13,470 --> 00:25:14,230
Where is the proof?

408
00:25:15,070 --> 00:25:16,400
I have achieved a scholarly honor.

409
00:25:17,520 --> 00:25:19,920
If you kill me unjustly without basis,

410
00:25:21,310 --> 00:25:22,800
won't it be hard to convince the public?

411
00:25:23,140 --> 00:25:25,660
[Ghostly Fire Case Volume 1]

412
00:25:29,920 --> 00:25:31,000
Shen Ci.

413
00:25:35,830 --> 00:25:36,590
So,

414
00:25:37,070 --> 00:25:38,590
you came back to Sunrise Garden

415
00:25:38,590 --> 00:25:39,830
because you are pissed at Mr. Pan.

416
00:25:40,710 --> 00:25:41,520
Correction.

417
00:25:41,920 --> 00:25:44,230
I'm not being angry,
it's about drawing a boundary.

418
00:25:44,680 --> 00:25:45,760
From now on,

419
00:25:45,760 --> 00:25:47,920
we will go our separate ways.

420
00:25:50,880 --> 00:25:51,430
Really?

421
00:25:51,590 --> 00:25:52,310
Of course.

422
00:25:57,000 --> 00:25:57,800
That's pretty good.

423
00:25:58,350 --> 00:25:59,560
Plenty of fish in the sea.

424
00:25:59,760 --> 00:26:01,710
Why would you fixate on the same guy?

425
00:26:05,590 --> 00:26:06,830
Look at the people around you.

426
00:26:07,040 --> 00:26:08,190
Young Master Zhuo is pretty good too.

427
00:26:17,710 --> 00:26:18,590
Did he confess to you?

428
00:26:19,350 --> 00:26:20,640
Did he tell you?

429
00:26:20,950 --> 00:26:21,920
I guessed it.

430
00:26:22,880 --> 00:26:24,110
So, he really did confess to you?

431
00:26:29,800 --> 00:26:30,950
You haven't noticed it, have you?

432
00:26:31,110 --> 00:26:32,400
His eyes are always on you.

433
00:26:32,760 --> 00:26:33,880
That's not how you look at a friend.

434
00:26:35,070 --> 00:26:36,950
Now I just want
to investigate the ripple pattern,

435
00:26:36,950 --> 00:26:38,350
so that I can be Yang Caiwei again.

436
00:26:46,460 --> 00:26:49,920
[Court]

437
00:26:49,920 --> 00:26:52,110
There was no evidence to prove
that Shen Ci was the murderer.

438
00:26:52,280 --> 00:26:54,350
But he was the only suspect in the case.

439
00:26:54,520 --> 00:26:56,110
At that time, he was sentenced
to be detained and tried later.

440
00:26:56,310 --> 00:26:57,710
Sir, I have been handling cases
for ten years,

441
00:26:57,830 --> 00:26:59,760
I must have arrested
about a thousand suspects.

442
00:26:59,920 --> 00:27:01,470
I've never seen someone this weird.

443
00:27:01,760 --> 00:27:02,560
What's weird about him?

444
00:27:02,680 --> 00:27:03,710
When he first came in,

445
00:27:03,880 --> 00:27:05,110
he was held with other prisoners.

446
00:27:05,280 --> 00:27:06,190
Within a few days,

447
00:27:06,280 --> 00:27:08,040
the vicious bandits

448
00:27:08,190 --> 00:27:09,680
all clamored to change cells.

449
00:27:09,800 --> 00:27:11,590
In the end, there was no option
but to hold him in solitary confinement.

450
00:27:11,710 --> 00:27:12,710
I have observed him secretly.

451
00:27:12,880 --> 00:27:14,070
He keeps talking to himself all day long.

452
00:27:14,160 --> 00:27:16,230
I don't know whether he
is chanting a mantra or a curse.

453
00:27:18,920 --> 00:27:20,950
Sir, please be careful.

454
00:27:21,190 --> 00:27:22,230
Don't be cursed by him.

455
00:27:26,430 --> 00:27:29,920
Come to me quickly.

456
00:27:31,950 --> 00:27:34,350
Come to me quickly.

457
00:27:35,680 --> 00:27:36,590
Hurry up.

458
00:27:37,800 --> 00:27:38,920
Come to me.

459
00:27:38,920 --> 00:27:41,310
Sir, look at him.
He is reciting a curse again.

460
00:27:46,190 --> 00:27:46,800
No.

461
00:27:48,920 --> 00:27:50,400
He's talking to a mouse.

462
00:27:55,310 --> 00:27:56,640
Forgive me for my lack of etiquette.

463
00:27:57,230 --> 00:27:58,470
I don't know who you are.

464
00:27:58,950 --> 00:28:00,110
Magistrate Pan Yue.

465
00:28:01,310 --> 00:28:02,640
Oh, Mr. Pan.

466
00:28:05,920 --> 00:28:07,590
You only have two steamed buns per meal.

467
00:28:08,110 --> 00:28:09,640
Why are you sharing with the mice?

468
00:28:14,310 --> 00:28:16,430
I'm imprisoned in this dark place.

469
00:28:17,400 --> 00:28:19,430
These insects and rats are a blessing
because they keep me company.

470
00:28:20,070 --> 00:28:21,400
I can pass the long days

471
00:28:22,000 --> 00:28:23,280
and talk with them to express my feelings.

472
00:28:24,950 --> 00:28:27,040
To you, it's a mouse.

473
00:28:28,400 --> 00:28:29,680
To me,

474
00:28:30,520 --> 00:28:32,000
it's an old friend.

475
00:29:03,070 --> 00:29:04,680
He is already on death row.

476
00:29:05,560 --> 00:29:07,400
Why is he still wearing
such heavy shackles?

477
00:29:08,520 --> 00:29:09,350
Unshackle him.

478
00:29:09,640 --> 00:29:11,830
Sir, this is a felon who knows witchcraft.

479
00:29:12,000 --> 00:29:12,800
What if he escapes?

480
00:29:12,800 --> 00:29:14,160
If he really knew witchcraft,

481
00:29:14,520 --> 00:29:16,070
not even ten chains would bind him.

482
00:29:16,520 --> 00:29:17,190
Unshackle him.

483
00:29:17,430 --> 00:29:18,040
Yes.

484
00:29:33,560 --> 00:29:34,560
Are you not afraid of me?

485
00:29:36,880 --> 00:29:37,800
Do I have to be?

486
00:29:47,430 --> 00:29:48,880
The pattern on the wall.

487
00:29:50,040 --> 00:29:51,520
Sir, you are here for this.

488
00:29:51,640 --> 00:29:52,190
Yes.

489
00:29:54,230 --> 00:29:55,470
Can you tell me honestly?

490
00:29:59,070 --> 00:30:00,310
If you are determined,

491
00:30:00,880 --> 00:30:02,310
you will find out

492
00:30:02,880 --> 00:30:04,040
once you've solved the case.

493
00:30:20,190 --> 00:30:22,310
Why are there so many stray cats
meowing outside?

494
00:30:40,560 --> 00:30:41,680
Quiet at last.

495
00:30:42,060 --> 00:30:43,460
I really want to have some chestnut cakes.

496
00:30:44,520 --> 00:30:47,070
Chestnut cakes.

497
00:30:47,160 --> 00:30:49,160
Freshly baked chestnut cakes.

498
00:30:49,680 --> 00:30:50,880
Take a look.

499
00:30:51,230 --> 00:30:53,070
Chestnut cakes.

500
00:31:01,950 --> 00:31:05,310
Why did the cake vendor come
at such a coincidental time?

501
00:31:05,920 --> 00:31:07,430
The cat meowing just now

502
00:31:07,950 --> 00:31:09,160
was also stopped suddenly.

503
00:31:09,710 --> 00:31:11,560
Could it be?

504
00:31:16,560 --> 00:31:17,430
Ling.

505
00:31:19,310 --> 00:31:21,640
I'm tired of eating your cooking
every day.

506
00:31:22,350 --> 00:31:24,350
Today, I want to eat

507
00:31:26,230 --> 00:31:28,950
freshly roasted lamb shank
with Huadiao wine.

508
00:31:38,160 --> 00:31:38,680
Here.

509
00:31:39,560 --> 00:31:41,190
Hurry, take it in while it's hot.

510
00:31:41,230 --> 00:31:41,880
Yes.

511
00:31:42,310 --> 00:31:44,470
Young Lady's guess was right.
It's really you.

512
00:31:44,760 --> 00:31:46,310
Miss... Miss Ling.

513
00:31:46,950 --> 00:31:47,920
Where is your Young Master?

514
00:31:52,140 --> 00:31:53,820
[Huadiao]

515
00:31:56,640 --> 00:31:57,590
Jiang.

516
00:31:59,400 --> 00:32:00,760
You don't have to be so nice to me.

517
00:32:01,110 --> 00:32:02,350
Didn't I tell you?

518
00:32:02,520 --> 00:32:03,190
I take you…

519
00:32:03,190 --> 00:32:04,590
As a friend. I know.

520
00:32:05,040 --> 00:32:06,160
But this is how I, Zhuo Lanjiang,

521
00:32:06,160 --> 00:32:07,310
treat my friends.

522
00:32:09,350 --> 00:32:09,920
I…

523
00:32:10,590 --> 00:32:11,430
Yang Caiwei.

524
00:32:11,680 --> 00:32:13,160
When did you become so bashful?

525
00:32:13,830 --> 00:32:15,350
How am I bashful?

526
00:32:15,760 --> 00:32:16,400
Yes.

527
00:32:16,680 --> 00:32:18,800
Look at this freshly roasted lamb shank
with Huadiao wine.

528
00:32:19,680 --> 00:32:20,350
Are you going to drink it?

529
00:32:21,860 --> 00:32:23,920
Of course. Why not?

530
00:32:30,350 --> 00:32:32,470
The victims of the Ghostly Fire case
are two dead and one injured.

531
00:32:33,280 --> 00:32:35,350
Shen Ci is the only suspect.

532
00:32:36,070 --> 00:32:37,880
The key to cracking the case

533
00:32:38,190 --> 00:32:39,590
is on him.

534
00:32:41,160 --> 00:32:42,520
But is he really someone

535
00:32:42,560 --> 00:32:44,760
who would use witchcraft
to harm his classmates?

536
00:32:54,040 --> 00:32:54,760
Am I right?

537
00:32:54,880 --> 00:32:55,640
Really.

538
00:32:59,160 --> 00:32:59,950
Come here.

539
00:33:00,000 --> 00:33:00,640
What's wrong?

540
00:33:00,800 --> 00:33:03,190
Unexpectedly, Miss Shangguan has left,

541
00:33:03,590 --> 00:33:06,070
but these plants are still not spared.

542
00:33:09,920 --> 00:33:11,430
For his sins.

543
00:33:24,190 --> 00:33:24,880
Young Master.

544
00:33:25,640 --> 00:33:26,230
Young Master.

545
00:33:28,070 --> 00:33:29,400
What are you doing?

546
00:33:33,190 --> 00:33:33,830
Nothing.

547
00:33:35,950 --> 00:33:36,680
Where are you going?

548
00:33:38,110 --> 00:33:39,830
Miss Yang's frame portrait is ready.

549
00:33:40,400 --> 00:33:41,110
I'll go.

550
00:33:41,950 --> 00:33:43,040
I wanted to go for a walk anyway.

551
00:33:45,830 --> 00:33:46,470
Take a look.

552
00:33:46,920 --> 00:33:47,590
Here's the money.

553
00:33:48,110 --> 00:33:48,710
Okay.

554
00:33:48,830 --> 00:33:49,400
Let's go.

555
00:33:49,430 --> 00:33:50,160
Take care.

556
00:33:56,160 --> 00:33:59,350
Mr. Pan, won't you have an iced drink
